---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Business Automations — LeadFair"
  description="Stop doing repetitive work manually. We connect your tools and automate follow-ups, scheduling, data entry, and more."
  headline="Stop Doing Work a Machine Should Do"
  subheadline="We find the repetitive tasks eating your time — follow-ups, data entry, scheduling, notifications — and automate them so they just happen."
  accentColor="accent"
>
  <!-- What We Automate -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">What We Can Automate</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">If you're doing it the same way every time, there's a good chance we can automate it.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Follow-Up Messages</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Automatically send follow-up emails or texts after a new lead comes in, an appointment is booked, or a form is submitted.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Appointment Reminders</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Reduce no-shows with automatic reminders via text or email. Customers can confirm, reschedule, or cancel without calling.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Data Sync</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Keep your CRM, calendar, spreadsheets, and other tools in sync. No more entering the same info in three different places.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Lead Routing</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">New leads from your website, phone, or ads automatically go to the right person or system — with all the info attached.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Notifications & Alerts</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Get notified when something important happens — a new review, a missed call, a high-value lead — so you can act fast.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Custom Workflows</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Got a process that's unique to your business? We can build custom automations that fit exactly how you work.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-14">How We Set It Up</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shrink-0">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Map Your Processes</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">We walk through your daily operations and identify the tasks that are repetitive, time-consuming, or easy to mess up.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shrink-0">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Build the Automations</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">We connect your existing tools and build the workflows. No need to switch software — we work with what you already use.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shrink-0">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Test & Refine</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">We test every automation with real scenarios, make sure nothing falls through the cracks, and adjust until it's running smoothly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who It's For -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-14">Who This Is For</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          <p class="text-text-light">Businesses spending hours on repetitive manual tasks</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          <p class="text-text-light">Owners who want their business to run without them</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          <p class="text-text-light">Teams juggling too many tools with no connection</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          <p class="text-text-light">Anyone who drops the ball on follow-ups or reminders</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
